@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Featured listings
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/featured

### Search by text
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=denim&page=1&limit=20

### Filtered search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?category=outerwear&type=retail&condition=used&gender=unisex&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=10000&sort=price_asc&page=1&limit=20

### Delivery estimate
GET {{baseUrl}}/delivery/estimate?region=Greater%20Accra&city=Accra&method=delivery

### Pickup estimate
GET {{baseUrl}}/delivery/estimate?region=Greater%20Accra&city=Accra&method=pickup
